    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it is in absolutely flawless condition inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh new-car smell. I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but I'm looking for a great new home for it. Grab this gem while you can!",
