    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with documented preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The drivetrain remains factory-spec, utilizing a longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal power distribution. The chassis retains its original rigidity, supported by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and pristine subframe bushings. Finished in Interlagos Blue, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage. This is a purist\u2019s example, offering linear power delivery and a visceral 8,400 RPM redline without the typical wear found in high-performance grand tourers.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
